about.summary: Methods for the inference on and the simulation of Gaussian fields are provided, as well as methods for the simulation of extreme value random fields.

name: r-randomfields
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "3.3.8" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-randomfields
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/RandomFields_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/RandomFields/RandomFields_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8a08e2fdae428e354a29fb6818ae781cc56235a6849a0d29574dc756f73199d0

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}      # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}grep              # [win]
    - {{ posix }}autoconf
    - {{ posix }}automake          # [not win]
    - {{ posix }}automake-wrapper  # [win]
    - {{ posix }}pkg-config
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-randomfieldsutils >=0.5.1
    - r-sp
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-randomfieldsutils >=0.5.1
    - r-sp

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('RandomFields')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('RandomFields')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://ms.math.uni-mannheim.de/de/publications/software/randomfields
  license: GPL (>= 3)
  summary: Methods for the inference on and the simulation of Gaussian fields are provided, as
    well as methods for the simulation of extreme value random fields.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - ocefpaf
